  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/429e40700ec456e967bc13fbdd853212.avif?t=1755193722\" width=616 height=399 /></span><br><br><strong>Nobody leaves here alive!</strong><br><br><strong>THE HOUSE OF THE DEAD: Remake</strong> is a remade version of the game introduced in 1997 in arcade platform. A classic arcade rail-shooter receives a whole new entourage and gameplay changes to suit modern gaming standards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/6c8b104a16b0d40b72e39ff70ed46cb7.webp?t=1755193722\" width=616 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/ce9932ef33ec6cd736af02c5b3897377.avif?t=1755193722\" width=616 height=69 /></span><br><br>• Well known arcade classic with modern graphics and controls<br>• True to the original gameplay<br>• Local 2-player multiplayer<br>• Multiple endings<br>• Photomode<br>• Achievements<br>• Armory with unlockable weapons<br>• Hordes of the undead monstrosities in a new game mode<br>• Gallery with encountered enemies and bosses<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/8dabbba07771ae79b5ca34ae7c7dc2f2.poster.avif?t=1755193722\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/8dabbba07771ae79b5ca34ae7c7dc2f2.webm?t=1755193722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/8dabbba07771ae79b5ca34ae7c7dc2f2.mp4?t=1755193722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/429e40700ec456e967bc13fbdd853212.avif?t=1755193722\" width=616 height=399 /></span><br><br><strong>Nobody leaves here alive!</strong><br><br><strong>THE HOUSE OF THE DEAD: Remake</strong> is a remade version of the game introduced in 1997 in arcade platform. A classic arcade rail-shooter receives a whole new entourage and gameplay changes to suit modern gaming standards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/6c8b104a16b0d40b72e39ff70ed46cb7.webp?t=1755193722\" width=616 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/ce9932ef33ec6cd736af02c5b3897377.avif?t=1755193722\" width=616 height=69 /></span><br><br>• Well known arcade classic with modern graphics and controls<br>• True to the original gameplay<br>• Local 2-player multiplayer<br>• Multiple endings<br>• Photomode<br>• Achievements<br>• Armory with unlockable weapons<br>• Hordes of the undead monstrosities in a new game mode<br>• Gallery with encountered enemies and bosses<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/8dabbba07771ae79b5ca34ae7c7dc2f2.poster.avif?t=1755193722\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/8dabbba07771ae79b5ca34ae7c7dc2f2.webm?t=1755193722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694600/extras/8dabbba07771ae79b5ca34ae7c7dc2f2.mp4?t=1755193722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
